headline: Wells Fargo Upgrades Cintas (CTAS) and Names it a Top Pick for 2026
summary: Cintas Corporation (NASDAQ:CTAS) is included among the 13 Best February Dividend Stocks to Buy. On January 14, Wells Fargo upgraded Cintas Corporation (NASDAQ:CTAS) to Overweight from Equal Weight and lifted its price target to $245 from $205.
